gov.usgs.anss.edgemom

Class OutputInfrastructure.AccreteMiniSeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.edgemom.OutputInfrastructure.AccreteMiniSeed
  • Enclosing class:
    OutputInfrastructure

    public final class OutputInfrastructure.AccreteMiniSeed
extends java.lang.Object
    The data comes here in EdgeBlocks with 512 bytes of payload. If a MiniSeed block is longer than 512, we need to accumulate several to build up the bigger block. The block with headers creates one of these, and each following block accretes until its done.
